Angelina Jolie has filed for divorce from Brad Pitt, the actress&#8217;s lawyer has confirmed.Robert Offer said the actress filed for &#8220;dissolution of marriage&#8221; on Monday, adding the &#8220;decision was made for the health of the family&#8221;.&#8220;She will not be commenting, and asks that the family be given its privacy at this time,&#8221; Offer added in the statement.The couple have been together since 2004 but only married in August 2014.The couple have six children together &#8211; Maddox, Pax, Zahara, Shiloh, and twins Knox and Vivienne.-BBC